<NSWLayout />
<br>
<br>
<div class="container mt-5">
    <h1 class="display-4 text-center">PM2.5 Sensor Moduli</h1>
    <p class="lead text-center">PM2.5 Sensor Moduli bilan Havodagi Chang Zarrachalarini Aniqlang</p>

    <div class="my-5">
        <h2>Umumiy Ma'lumot</h2>
        <p>PM2.5 Sensor Moduli havodagi mayda chang zarrachalarini aniqlash uchun mo'ljallangan. Bu datchik havo sifati monitoringi, avtomatlashtirish tizimlari va boshqa turli xil loyihalarda keng qo'llanilishi mumkin. U Arduino va boshqa mikrokontrollerlar bilan mos keladi.</p>
        <img src="images/nsw_pm25sensor.jpg" alt="PM2.5 Sensor Moduli" class="img-fluid rounded shadow my-3" style="max-width: 400px;">
    </div>

    <div class="my-5">
        <h2>Asosiy Xususiyatlari</h2>
        <ul>
            <li>Ishlash kuchlanishi: 5V DC</li>
            <li>PM2.5 aniqlash diapazoni: 0-500 µg/m³</li>
            <li>O'lchov aniqligi: ±10%</li>
            <li>Modul hajmi: 48 x 37 x 12 mm</li>
        </ul>
    </div>

    <div class="my-5">
        <h2>Ilovalar</h2>
        <p>PM2.5 Sensor Moduli quyidagi turli loyihalarda ishlatilishi mumkin:</p>
        <ul>
            <li>Havo Sifatini Monitoring</li>
            <li>Avtomatlashtirish Tizimlari</li>
            <li>Xavfsizlik Tizimlari</li>
            <li>DIY Gadjetlar</li>
            <li>Ta'lim Loyiha</li>
        </ul>
    </div>

    <div class="my-5">
        <h2>Pin Tafsilotlari</h2>
        <p>PM2.5 Sensor Moduli portida quyidagi pinlar mavjud:</p>
        <table class="table table-bordered">
            <thead>
                <tr>
                    <th>Pin</th>
                    <th>Vazifasi</th>
                </tr>
            </thead>
            <tbody>
                <tr>
                    <td>GND</td>
                    <td>Manfiy to'k</td>
                </tr>
                <tr>
                    <td>VCC</td>
                    <td>Quvvatlantirish manbai</td>
                </tr>
                <tr>
                    <td>TX</td>
                    <td>Ma'lumot uzatish</td>
                </tr>
                <tr>
                    <td>RX</td>
                    <td>Ma'lumot qabul qilish</td>
                </tr>
            </tbody>
        </table>
    </div>

    <div class="my-5">
        <h2>Simlarni Ulash Rejimi</h2>
        <p>● RJ25 bilan ulanish</p>
        <p>PM2.5 Sensor Moduli RJ25 porti orqali ulanishi mumkin. Makeblock Orion-da RJ25 portidan foydalanganda, uni mos keluvchi portga ulashingiz kerak:</p>
        <img src="images/pm25sensor_rj25.jpg" alt="PM2.5 Sensor RJ25 Ulash" class="img-fluid rounded shadow my-3" style="max-width: 400px;">

        <p>● Dupont simi bilan ulanish</p>
        <p>Dupont simidan modulni Arduino UNO asos paneliga ulash uchun foydalanilganda, uning TX va RX pinlarini Arduino RX va TX pinlariga quyidagicha ulash lozim:</p>
        <img src="images/pm25sensor_dupont.jpg" alt="PM2.5 Sensor Dupont Ulash" class="img-fluid rounded shadow my-3" style="max-width: 400px;">
    </div>

    <div class="my-5">
        <h2>Dasturlash Bo'yicha Qo'llanma</h2>
        <p>Arduino Dasturlash</p>
        <p>Agar dastur yozish uchun Arduino dan foydalansangiz, PM2.5 Sensor Modulini boshqarish uchun quyidagi koddan foydalanishingiz mumkin:</p>
        <pre><code class="language-cpp">
// Arduino dastur kodi
#include &lt;SoftwareSerial.h>

SoftwareSerial pmSerial(10, 11); // RX, TX

void setup() {
    Serial.begin(9600);
    pmSerial.begin(9600);
    Serial.println("PM2.5 Sensor Ishlayapti...");
}

void loop() {
    if (pmSerial.available()) {
        int pm25Value = pmSerial.read();
        Serial.print("PM2.5 Qiymati: ");
        Serial.println(pm25Value);
    }
    delay(1000);
}
        </code></pre>
    </div>

    <div class="my-5">
        <h3>Prinsipiy Tahlil</h3>
        <p>PM2.5 Sensor Moduli havodagi mayda chang zarrachalarini aniqlash uchun mo'ljallangan. Bu modulning asosiy funktsiyasi havo sifati monitoringi va avtomatlashtirish tizimlarida chang zarrachalarini aniqlash va nazorat qilishdir. TX va RX pinlari orqali ma'lumot uzatish va qabul qilish amalga oshiriladi.</p>
    </div>


